    "body": "Using `HTML`, it's pretty straight-forward:\r\n\r\n```py\r\nfrom IPython.display import display, HTML\r\n\r\nHTML('''<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: row;\">\r\n    <img src=\"../giphy.gif\">\r\n    <img src=\"../giphy.gif\">\r\n    <img src=\"../giphy.gif\">\r\n</div>''')\r\n```"
